✅ 🗓️ Weekly Closures entries must be CATEGORIES (Museums, Palaces, Stores), not specific venue names — city-wide weekly patterns only; per-venue quirks belong on the stop block (per Weekly Closures - Extra Section.html ; caught 2026-05-08)
✅ 🗓️ Weekly Closures — every stop with a 🚫 Closed row appears in the Weekly Closures section (per Weekly Closures - Extra Section.html — section is the single source of truth; missing stops leave the reader without the at-a-glance closure warning; accent-insensitive + 3-char matching + name-mismatch hints added 2026-05-08)
✅ 🗓️ Weekly Closures — "Closed" must be capitalised in every entry (spec format: "Category · Closed Day"; lowercase "closed" is authoring drift) (Weekly Closures - Extra Section.html § 2)
✅ 🗓️ Weekly Closures — "Closed" appears exactly once per entry (multiple days are a list after one "Closed", e.g. "Closed Monday & Tuesday") (Weekly Closures - Extra Section.html § 2)
✅ 🗓️ Weekly Closures — no <a> links inside .stop-row entries (entries are plain text + <strong> only; links are format drift) (Weekly Closures - Extra Section.html § 2)
