✅ 🗓️ Weekly Closures — category name must not end with punctuation (. , ; :) (the middle-dot separator follows immediately; no extra punctuation) (Weekly Closures - Extra Section.html § 2)
✅ 🗓️ Weekly Closures — no tilde (~) in entries (tilde is globally banned outside ⏰ context) (Weekly Closures - Extra Section.html § 2)
✅ 🗓️ Weekly Closures — no build annotations in entries ([UPDATE]/[CHECK]/[TBD]/🔴 etc. must be stripped before shipping) (Weekly Closures - Extra Section.html § 2)
