✅ 🗓️ Weekly Closures — negative-finding line must be inside <div class="extras-empty"> (bare text / <p> is structural drift) (Weekly Closures - Extra Section.html § 3)
✅ 🗓️ Weekly Closures — negative-finding line must end with a period (spec: "No notable city-wide weekly closures in [City].") (Weekly Closures - Extra Section.html § 3)
✅ Prices — zero money figures anywhere in a shipped guide (§Prices — on-demand categories only)
✅ No unfilled placeholder tokens ({TBD}, {TODO}, {City}, etc.) in shipped guide
